trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of namespace objects.
trans-unit.target: 包含命名空间对象的集合。

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 此类不能被继承。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceCollection> contains <xref:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo> objects.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceCollection>包含<xref:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo>对象。

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo> object is the same as an `Import` (`<%@ Import %>`) directive that applies to all pages and controls in the scope of the configuration file.
trans-unit.target: 每个<xref:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo>对象等同于`Import`(`<%@ Import %>`) 应用于所有页面和控件的配置文件的作用域中的指令。

trans-unit.source: The `Import` directive allows you to import a namespace into your ASP.NET page, making all its classes available for use on your page.
trans-unit.target: `Import`指令允许你将命名空间导入你的 ASP.NET 页上，打开你页上进行所有类可供使用。

trans-unit.target: 下面的配置文件摘录演示如何以声明方式指定的多个属性的值<xref:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceCollection>类。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that determines whether the Visual Basic namespace is imported without having to specify it.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置一个值，该值确定是否可以导入 Visual Basic 命名空间而无需指定它。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the Visual Basic namespace is imported automatically; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果自动导入 Visual Basic 命名空间，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The default is <see langword="true" />.
trans-unit.target: 默认值为 <see langword="true" />。

trans-unit.source: For ASP.NET pages written using Visual Basic the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic> namespace is automatically imported unless the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceCollection.AutoImportVBNamespace%2A> property is `false`.
trans-unit.target: 使用 Visual Basic 编写的 ASP.NET 页面<xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic>命名空间会自动导入的除非<xref:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceCollection.AutoImportVBNamespace%2A>属性是`false`。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo" /> object at the specified index in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置集合中指定索引处的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo" /> 对象。

trans-unit.source: <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo" /> object at the specified index, or <see langword="null" /> if there is no object at that index.
trans-unit.target: 指定索引处的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo" /> 对象；如果该索引处没有对象，则为 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: This property overwrites the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo> object if it already exists at the specified index; otherwise, a new object is created and added to the collection.
trans-unit.target: 此属性将会覆盖<xref:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo>对象已存在的指定索引处的情况; 否则为创建新对象并将添加到集合。

trans-unit.source: Removes the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo" /> object with the specified key from the collection.
trans-unit.target: 从集合中移除具有指定键的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.NamespaceInfo" /> 对象。

trans-unit.source: If the specified element is defined in a higher-level configuration file, this method inserts a `remove` element into the appropriate section of the configuration file at the level of the current application.
trans-unit.target: 如果指定的元素在更高级的配置文件中定义的此方法将插入`remove`元素插入当前应用程序级别的配置文件的相应节。

trans-unit.source: If the element is defined in the current configuration file, its entry is removed from the configuration file.
trans-unit.target: 如果该元素定义在当前的配置文件中，从配置文件中移除其项。

trans-unit.source: The object to remove must exist in the collection; if it does not, a <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationException> is thrown.
trans-unit.target: 要移除的对象必须存在于集合;如果不是，请<xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationException>引发。
